➜LOL新重装辅助英雄登场：双形态铁骑芮尔技能数值曝光！
http://www.sohu.com/a/433906817_634138	11838
<p class="ql-align-justify">今日LOL测试服更新了全新的英雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>新英雄：芮尔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>英雄形象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201124/833adcf5ff454f4da7725b7f80f6b805.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201124/f4f09a5c629f4fa2b60ef7028776f974.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201124/621be9973a704e2fbe63de74b2933cb3.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
